[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: E, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 2, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "eccef3be0d4472bbae180a788298cebdd84a4a40dd1166d821ba8f4662d88524"]
[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_transfers"]
[Student "S"]
{You open 1NT and partner responds 2\D.  

You complete the transfer by bidding 2\H.

Partner now says 3\C.  

Partner has 5 \Hs and probably 4 \Cs.

He is interested in slam and wants help from you in either of his suits. You have a minimum 1NT opener and no help for him so you try to dampen his enthusiasm by bidding 3NT. It works.}

